The paper focuses on the development of Explainable AI systems, which falls under the category of Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC). The study also involves assessing and understanding intelligent agents (cs.AI), and information retrieval (cs.IR) is used as a lens to analyze the participants' foraging behavior. Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) may also be relevant due to the use of language and data analysis in the study.
